headline: YouTuber Logan Paul cashes in $16.5 million for his Pokémon card. It’s vindication for the ‘armchair quarterbacks yelling from the sidelines,’ he says
summary: Social media mogul Logan Paul just set a world record for the most expensive trading card ever sold. He earned a 200% return on his initial investment.
